# Sound Effects Directory

Place audio files here:
- click.mp3      - Button click chirp (0.3 volume)
- hover.mp3      - Subtle hover blip (0.15 volume)
- success.mp3    - Positive confirmation (0.4 volume)
- error.mp3      - Error/failure sound (0.4 volume)
- alert.mp3      - Attention notification (0.5 volume)
- turn-end.mp3   - Turn completion chime (0.4 volume)
- combat.mp3     - Combat initiated (0.5 volume)
- build.mp3      - Construction queued (0.3 volume)

Recommended sources (free, CC0/Public Domain):
- https://freesound.org - Search "sci-fi beep", "UI click"
- https://pixabay.com/sound-effects/ - "Interface", "Notification"
- https://kenney.nl/assets - UI Audio pack
